<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <title></title>
  <meta name="description" content="user-creation" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }

    .card {
      box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background-color: white;
      margin: 25px;
    }

    .card-header {
      border-top: 3px solid rgb(108, 180, 59);
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 10px 60px 0;
    }

    .card-footer {
      border-top: 1px dashed rgb(108, 180, 59);
      padding: 10px 10px 10px;
    }

    td {
      border: 0px dashed #6cb43b;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .capitalize {
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }

    .lg-button {
      border-radius: 23px;
      color: #6cb43b;
      border: 1px solid #6cb43b;
      font-size: 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
      text-align: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    #disagree {
      color: red;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .consent {
      text-align: justify;
      text-justify: inter-word;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <img style="margin-left: 45%" width="128" height="128" src="<%= logo %>" alt="logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="card-content">
      Dear <strong>
        <%=firstName%>
          <%=lastName%>,
      </strong>
      <br /><br />
      <strong> Welcome to SCANDIDATE!</strong>
      <br /><br /><br />


      <div class="consent">

        <strong> SCANDIDATE</strong> is a hiring platform for recruiters to view career tracks of potential
        candidates
        in a simplified
        way. This is the first medium through which jobseekers' educational and professional credentials
        can
        be
        previewed by
        prospective
        employers.

      </div>
      <br /><br />

      <div class="consent">
        We would like to notify you that your listing has been created on SCANDIDATE by an ex-employer or an
        educational
        institute you have graduated from.

      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="consent">
        Request you to click on the buttons below to enable sharing of your career / educational records on
        SCANDIDATE
        with prospective employers.
      </div>
      <br /><br />


      <div class="consent">
        Please be informed that the platform captures no sensitive personal information and any information on
        our
        platform can
        be accessed only by the member organizations.
      </div>
      <br /><br />


      <div class="consent">
        Your consent shall initiate your SCANDIDATE journey - a first-of-its-kind wherein you can let your
        credentials
        speak for
        you.
      </div>
      </Your>
      <br /><br />


      Wish you the very best.<br /><br />

    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="card-footer">
      <p>
        Regards,<br />
        <b>Scandidate.in</b>
        <br /><br />
        <a class="lg-button" href="<%= agreelink %>" target="_blank">Agree</a>
        <a class="lg-button" id="disagree" href="<%=disagreelink%>" target="_blank">
          Disagree
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>